Package algebraPackage

Class AlgebraMatrix

java.lang.Object
algebraPackage.AlgebraMatrix
public class AlgebraMatrix extends Object
Class that contains different methods to make operations and transformations to matrices. This loads a method that was chosen by the user in MatrixMenu. In case that the entry in any method is not correct, the user will be returned to Mathall main menu MatrixMenu.
Version:
27.06.2022
Author:
Filipondios
